on the effect of white-nose
syndrome on bats

41:42.266 --> 41:44.635 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
at Mammoth Cave National Park.

41:44.668 --> 41:54.712 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You can find that report on
